       'Private equity investments may be illiquid for extended periods',
       'Direct securities are subject to market and company-specific risk',
       'These investments are suitable only for investors with appropriate risk tolerance',
       'The FSP will only invest in alternatives consistent with the agreed mandate parameters',
      ].forEach(b=>bullet(b));
